    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that’s the thing, it's not even about needing therapy or \"connection\" anymore. it's just that the effort to stay visible feels so exhausting. like, i'm tired of trying to prove i exist to a world that doesn't care. it feels more like i'm just waiting for the battery to run out. if i just let it fade, wouldn't that be easier than fighting to be seen by people who wouldn't even notice the absence?",
